<p>
  <span class="nym">Erhard</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German, Old Saxon</span> <i>era</i> 'honor' + <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>hard</i>, <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>hart</i> 'strong, hard'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 7th C German saint.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


